And replacing that infrastructure is also a key ingredient in several of our jurisdictions. In addition to that, around the security of the overall system as well. So when we look at where we're going, electrifying our vehicle fleet, electrification of our system, the replacement of our gas system and also ensuring that it's secure are really our opportunities across each of our jurisdictions.

